PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of MAURICE B. KRAUT, of Winnipeg, Manitoba, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Farm Credit Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Peter Rampton, whose term has expired.
